The Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV) sub-category is also likely as it specifically deals with convolutional neural networks, which are commonly used in computer vision tasks. 

The Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category is also possible as the paper proposes a new method for optimizing neural networks, which is a common topic in AI research.
